name: src/ReactNipple.js
propTypes
description:
Component propTypes

Any additional (unknown) props will be passed along as attributes of the created DOM element.

properties.name: className
properties.description: A css classname for the DOM element

properties.name: options
properties.description: An object with nipplejs options, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#options

properties.name: static
properties.description: A shortcut for setting the options `{mode: 'static', position: {top: '50%', left: '50%'}}`. Will override values in the `options` object.

properties.name: onCreated
properties.description: Callback that is invoked with the created instance

properties.name: onDestroy
properties.description: Callback that is invoked with the instance that is going to be destroyed

properties.name: onStart
properties.description: Callback for the 'start' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#start

properties.name: onEnd
properties.description: Callback for the 'end' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#end

properties.name: onMove
properties.description: Callback for the 'move' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#move

properties.name: onDir
properties.description: Callback for the 'dir' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#dir

properties.name: onPlain
properties.description: Callback for the 'plain' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#plain

properties.name: onShown
properties.description: Callback for the 'shown' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#shown

properties.name: onHidden
properties.description: Callback for the 'hidden' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#hidden

properties.name: onPressure
properties.description: Callback for the 'pressure' event handler, see https://github.com/yoannmoinet/nipplejs#pressure
